snippet.title: Encapsulation in Java - Learn Encapsulation
snippet.description:
New course coming soon! Learn Java Fast launches on July 1st, 2020. Stay informed and join the waitlist: https://course.alexlorenlee.com/courses/learn-java-fast

- Encapsulation is accessing private variables using methods. These are also known as setters and getters!

I hope you enjoyed this video on how to use encapsulation in java :) -
